BIB                 12         18
TITLE      Neutron yields from the 7Li(p,n')7Be* reaction near
           threshold
AUTHOR     (S.G.Buccino,C.E.Hollandsworth,P.R.Bevington)
REFERENCE  (J,NP,53,375,1964)
INSTITUTE  (1USADKE)
FACILITY   (VDG,1USADKE)
SAMPLE     Thin film of LiF evaporated onto a 0.25 mm tantalum end
           cap. The target was 8 keV thick to protons of 1.9 MeV.
METHOD     (TOF,PHD)
DETECTOR   (SCIN) 6Li glass scintillator 6.4 mm thick by 3.8 cm
           diameter viewed by a 6810A photomultiplier.
           (LONGC) McKibben long counter for monitoring.
MONITOR    (3-LI-7(P,N)4-BE-7,PAR,SIG)
MONIT-REF  (A1480004,P.R.Bevington+,J,PR,121,871,1961)
REL-REF    (A,A1483002,R.Batchelor+,J,PPS/A,68,(431),1081,1955)
HISTORY    (19800815C) Compilation produced by RFNC-VNIIEF Sarov
           (19990323U)CNPD: corrected 4-dig. year and lower cases.
           (20260318A) SD: Corrections in all Subents.
