BIB                  4          7
REACTION   (3-LI-7(P,N)4-BE-7,PAR,SIG)
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) Errors are +-10% for the low-energy points
            (2.4 to 2.7 MeV) and +-15%  for the higher energies.
           No other information about source of uncertainty.
